      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "星見漁港のどこかに囚われているらしいの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They seem to be held captive somewhere in Hoshimi Fishing Port…",
